The paper discusses a system for organizing scientific publications into a hierarchical concept structure, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. This suggests that the paper could fall under several sub-categories, including Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Deep Learning (cs.DL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Computational Linguistics (cs.CL).
